# Unsplash — server-side only. Used to auto-suggest a cover photo for a trip
# or city leg. Sign up at unsplash.com/developers (free "Demo" app, no
# review needed for personal use) and use the Access Key. Without this, the
# auto-suggest step is skipped silently and manual photo upload still works.
